caption.title: Plots of similarity of the near-complete polyprotein coding alignment (9931 nt) of AEFV-Turkey (MK251047), with individual functional units indicated (GapStrip: On, Reps: 1000, Kimura (2-parameter), T/t: 2.0).
caption.p: The curves indicate comparisons between the target and reference genomes (AEFV-Bangkok: KJ741266 AEFV-Narita21: NC012932, AEFV-SPFLD: KC181923). Each point plotted is the percent identity within a sliding window 200 bp wide centered on the position plotted, with a step size between points of 20 bp.
